{
  "texts": [
    "We agree with Mellon et al.",
    "(109) that the availability of large language models makes the use of open-ended questions in future questionnaires more attractive.",
    "Nevertheless, there are some limitations to using ChatGPT.",
    "While ChatGPT is proficient in summarization and sentiment analysis [e.g., (47, 54, 110) ], it may lack domain-specific expertise (111).",
    "Moreover, its output can be sensitive to the specific wording of the prompt (47)."
  ]
}